Increase your astronomical knowledge and help younger girls discover the mysteries above us! Helping to deliver the course material in the astronomy class is much easier if you have an understanding of what it is all about. Come see the new activities before anyone else. Get some personal time with telescopes to view what is in the night sky! This event costs $10.00 per girl, $7 per adult. This is a day-time program and no telescopic viewing is planned with this training.

**Girls must be previously PA trained to register for this session.  All adults attending this session must be registered & approved volunteers, Adult ratios are per Safety Activity Checkpoints..
